Prediction of Ratings from Product Reviews

1. We have scraped Electronics Product Reviews from 2 most used websites: Amazon and Flipkart (Using Selenium webdriver)
2. Then we performed Text modelling using Latent Dirichlet Allocation
3. We will train a traditional Machine Learning model using scikit-learn
4. We will train a LSTM model with normal Embedding layer
5. We will finally look at HuggingFace Transformers library

